                     <interp inst="t18150405-125-person1102" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . The prisoner was my <rs id="t18150405-125-deflabel682" type="occupation">clerk</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150405-125-defend1098 t18150405-125-deflabel682"></join>. This receipt is his hand writing; he never accounted to me for the money. This is the day-book, in which Mr. Lee is debitted; he ought to have entered it in the cash-book as paid; he has not; he never accompted to me for this seven pounds two shillings.</p>
               <p>The prisoner called three witnesses, who gave him a good character.</p>
